## ðŸ› ï¸ Tools & Frameworks

### Installed on Kali Linux (Attacker Machine)
- **Nmap** - Network scanning
- **Metasploit Framework** - Exploitation
- **Burp Suite** - Web proxy
- **John the Ripper** - Password cracking
- **Wireshark** - Packet analysis
- **GDB** - Debugging
- **Ghidra** - Reverse engineering
- **IDA Pro Free** - Disassembler
- **sqlmap** - SQL injection automation
- **BeEF** - Browser exploitation

### Custom Tools (Developed Here)
- **Port Scanner Pro** - Multi-threaded Python scanner
- **Payload Factory** - Generate test payloads in multiple languages
- **Log Monitor** - Real-time log analysis for defense
- **Lab Orchestrator** - Manage VM states and snapshots

